{
  "text": "Pore plate method was performed on medium contains 5g glucose, 5g peptone, 5g sodium chloride, 3g beef extract and 15g agar, dissolved in distilled water up to 1L [CITATION_1] . 0.3ml of algal extract was introduced into 10mm well diameter. For the control, 0.3ml of DMSO was used. Inhibition zones were read one day after incubation at 37\u00b0C. Each assay was repeated three times and the mean values were recorded.",
